    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of regular use, while the interior remains in great shape with no major tears or stains. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, the transmission shifts well, and all major electronics are fully functional. It is a reliable, solid driver that is ready for the road without needing any immediate repairs.",
